<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Passwords</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <p>Strong passwords are a critical part of securing your accounts. Tips:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Use passwords of at least 12 characters.</li>
            <li>Include a mix of uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Consider using a password manager to generate and store passwords securely.</p>
        <p>Check out these options:
            <a href="https://www.lastpass.com" target="_blank">LastPass</a>,
            <a href="https://www.dashlane.com" target="_blank">Dashlane</a>,
            <a href="https://bitwarden.com" target="_blank">Bitwarden</a>
        </p>
        <a href="index.html">Back to Home</a>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Cybersecurity Awareness Tool</p>
    </footer>
