<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Second-Factor Authentication (2FA)</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <p>2FA adds an extra layer of security to your accounts by requiring a second verification step. Benefits:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Protects against unauthorized access.</li>
            <li>Easy to set up with most modern apps.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Recommended apps for 2FA:
            <a href="https://authy.com" target="_blank">Authy</a>,
            <a href="https://www.google.com/landing/2step/" target="_blank">Google Authenticator</a>,
            <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/security/mobile-authenticator-app" target="_blank">Microsoft Authenticator</a>
        </p>
        <a href="index.html">Back to Home</a>
    </main>
